lac.cnclib.sddl.message

Class ApplicationMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • lac.cnclib.sddl.message.ApplicationMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Message
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ServiceMessage

    public class ApplicationMessage
extends java.lang.Object
implements Message
    Class that implements the message abstraction. Represents topics exchanged by the DDS SDDL infrastructure. The messages are used by the applications.
    Author:
    Rafael
